    java.lang.Runnable

    public class InternManCLUI
extends CommandLineUI<InternMan>
    Extends the CommandLineUI framework class to provide a command line user interface for the InternMan Internship Management system. The class also provides a main entry point for invoking an implementation of the InternMan system.
    Author:
    tws, jsinger
